%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: CODE-Dialog_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0a78892ee6a7ac44eaef6f692257751c, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 259275231232
    m_Localized: What an interesting universe. I've never seen such unstable things-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 260965535744
    m_Localized: Oh? You can't progress?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 263586975744
    m_Localized: There. That should do it for you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 265453441024
    m_Localized: That's the last time I'll be helping you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 420651077632
    m_Localized: Who am I? That I don't know myself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 422211358720
    m_Localized: Oh don't worry about that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 423234768896
    m_Localized: I'm sure we'll meet someday, you just won't know about it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 475630014464
    m_Localized: You seem surprised to see me here?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 476238188544
    m_Localized: I'm just recouping information, nothing too drastic.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 476858945536
    m_Localized: This place seems really unstable though, so get going before it's
      too late.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 536212541440
    m_Localized: '[Your communication with this glyph fizzles out...]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1187487289344
    m_Localized: You've finally made it here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1190188421120
    m_Localized: (Lumi! God damnit, took you long enough to point them here.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1191698370560
    m_Localized: So, you! Go on, a trial awaits you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1267736907776
    m_Localized: BEHOLD!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1268881952768
    m_Localized: That's right, good luck crossing it. I've already won.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1282156924928
    m_Localized: Unfair? Yeah, sorry. I don't make the rules.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1438260531200
    m_Localized: WHAT THE HELL
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1438847733760
    m_Localized: You aren't supposed to do that- What, I mean, what?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1439854366720
    m_Localized: This is so stupid! I didn't account for this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1530740740096
    m_Localized: Fire, then! Have at you, more fire! More! More!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1564555218944
    m_Localized: IM ON FIRE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1565188558848
    m_Localized: TOO MUCH FIRE, TOO MUCH FIRE!!!!!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1566019031040
    m_Localized: AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1644028891136
    m_Localized: Guh...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1686814986240
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1687679012864
    m_Localized: Y-you've bested me...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1689314791424
    m_Localized: Scram...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1688551428096
    m_Localized: Take y-your victory and go somewhere else.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1832722239488
    m_Localized: '[You decide to move on, they look warm and comfy]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 271917223383040
    m_Localized: Welcome to our A Directionless Cycle's official trivia!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272072446185472
    m_Localized: I've worked very very very hard on this, and chose only the best
      questions!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272073175994368
    m_Localized: Let's start simple.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272073779974144
    m_Localized: How many main levels are between W1 and The Core?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272282081693696
    m_Localized: What is the name of the level where you get fragment 4?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272281490296832
    m_Localized: Let's move on...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272280861151232
    m_Localized: Trick question! I said between, so inbetween them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272474327617536
    m_Localized: Ha! Trick question again, I asked for the level name.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272474914820096
    m_Localized: Which... is...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272475497828352
    m_Localized: Did I get you twice? I'm really sorry if I did.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272476156334080
    m_Localized: I promise, no weird stuff from now on. Let's go!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272476760313856
    m_Localized: Is the code "CBA" a valid code you can input on the title screen?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272671283744768
    m_Localized: Fire? Surely it can't get any worse than this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272670176448512
    m_Localized: This isn't supposed to...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272661276135424
    m_Localized: Uh...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272787935727616
    m_Localized: '[The carvings are on fire.]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272860048396288
    m_Localized: Yeah! Totally, just come this way!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272912221343744
    m_Localized: Uh... Please don't break out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272911613169664
    m_Localized: Shit! My questions!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 272909037867008
    m_Localized: What is- Wait, oh shit-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273064394887168
    m_Localized: Okay, fine. You can take that, I guess.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273070598262784
    m_Localized: What are the positions the prompter has been in so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273068446584832
    m_Localized: 'Let''s just keep going:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273337242750976
    m_Localized: Do take your time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273334910717952
    m_Localized: They lie... Can you figure it out? Surely...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273655942746112
    m_Localized: Of course im lying. But so is the prompt.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273606403821568
    m_Localized: I would never lie. Bottom is lying.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273767284740096
    m_Localized: Just pick a path! 50/50 chance, right?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273766131306496
    m_Localized: I'm totally not running out of ideas...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273765443440640
    m_Localized: Uh... uh!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273850277433344
    m_Localized: Screw you. Might aswell ram yourself against the wall, I am NOT
      helping you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 273888604983296
    m_Localized: Yeah, as top said. Go run into a wall or something. That'll teach
      you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 274010239799296
    m_Localized: And... As for the grand finale!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 274012534083584
    m_Localized: Are you in the same X axis as the screen you started in?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 274013091926016
    m_Localized: No pressure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718000584003584
    m_Localized: I am NOT sorry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717999766114304
    m_Localized: btw,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717998780452864
    m_Localized: You will get NOTHING from beating this, this is merely torture.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717997908037632
    m_Localized: Then, head down, straight middle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717996783964160
    m_Localized: It is around ~12 screens with width + height combined, and you need
      to find two buttons.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717996058349568
    m_Localized: An invisible maze.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717995387260928
    m_Localized: This entire level is just a maze.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718460468465664
    m_Localized: There's a button to your left-ish, though.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718459889651712
    m_Localized: btw this entire room is a dead end <3
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718510921748480
    m_Localized: Are you having fun yet?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718510326157312
    m_Localized: Button got!!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718587711066112
    m_Localized: Go get them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718586813485056
    m_Localized: Woah.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40853726998695936
    m_Localized: Yo!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40860066936655872
    m_Localized: Welcome to the dev room. In here, you'll hear me (Lumi, the developer)
      talk briefly about the game.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40860085248987136
    m_Localized: Did you get here by accident? I would recommend to leave and find
      your way after beating the game!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40860096024154112
    m_Localized: The code for this level is very well hidden, but in plain sight.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40860107889840128
    m_Localized: If you haven't found it, don't worry! You're welcome here anyways.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40860112268693504
    m_Localized: So... Have at you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719719635095552
    m_Localized: The Gummi version of ADC... The best version.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719775180263424
    m_Localized: A relic of the past- Okay, I'm joking, we've got Github.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719783484985344
    m_Localized: ADC was meant to be a simple sokoban game to test the waters with
      Unity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719788845305856
    m_Localized: It still is, but it's grown a lot closer to me that I expected.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719794327261184
    m_Localized: That has been mostly because of how much time I've poured into this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719800522248192
    m_Localized: The game started to spiral out of control after deciding to make
      the cycle ability go into other screens.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719806335553536
    m_Localized: Why?? The game was already finished, why would I ever do that???
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719811402272768
    m_Localized: I suppose, part of me wanted to make something bigger. And hey,
      it paid off.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719817232355328
    m_Localized: After adding cycling, and multiple screens, I think it took me around
      3-4 months to rework everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719823423148032
    m_Localized: Would definitely do it all again! That was really fun.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52719829270007808
    m_Localized: Hopefully no one ruined the cycling reveal for you. I would... bite
      them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52720401725394944
    m_Localized: ...Yeah, not much to see here, let's keep the ball rolling!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725279080189952
    m_Localized: This is most of the game's flowchart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725307404324864
    m_Localized: It has been under very heavy reworks, due to the project scope changing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725313905496064
    m_Localized: One of the things that I really, REALLY wanted to do, was to add
      secrets inside hint levels.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725318796054528
    m_Localized: Sadly, I don't think it would've hit as good as I felt, so I had
      to scrap it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725322424127488
    m_Localized: There was also supposed to be one "level" per artifact collected,
      that would be required to enter the core.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725327331463168
    m_Localized: ...I was running out of level ideas by that point, haha.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725358407061504
    m_Localized: Lastly, I also wanted to hide more codes in plain sight, like the
      one you used to get here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52725363779964928
    m_Localized: That would've been wayyyy too much work. So I settled for this instead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727719259148288
    m_Localized: Did you know?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727738372591616
    m_Localized: ADC was meant to be my final school project!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727746173997056
    m_Localized: I actually got a good grade, and a lot of feedback to expand upon
      it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727754285780992
    m_Localized: I will say, I probably didn't add as many mechanics as I thought
      from the beginning, but that's a good thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727759159562240
    m_Localized: Trust me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727764251447296
    m_Localized: So, this project was supposed to be a month only, but ended up taking
      wayyy too long.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727768680632320
    m_Localized: Overscoping and overscoping until I had to cut content! It was too
      exhausting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52727775198580736
    m_Localized: I'm very satisfied, though.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729490564059136
    m_Localized: Lumi!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729516992368640
    m_Localized: The original game's story was about-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729523615174656
    m_Localized: No, it wasn't about Lumi. But sometimes I'd like to think it was.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729528954523648
    m_Localized: It was about "trying to stop the universe from collapsing".
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729532427407360
    m_Localized: Apparently from whatever universe this was from, that was like a
      super common thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729537330548736
    m_Localized: Funny how the entire story changed to "destroy what's left of a
      game", ironic.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729542741200896
    m_Localized: Wondering who the canon game developer is? I don't know!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729547371712512
    m_Localized: My headcanon is that Lumi made it... But, oh well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729551842840576
    m_Localized: I'm sure It'll end up surfacing someday in whatever next game I
      make...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729556322357248
    m_Localized: Not exactly the next one, just one of them, I'm sure!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729560726376448
    m_Localized: I actually wasn't sure what image to use here, so... Have Lumi?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52729572352987136
    m_Localized: Alright, say bye to him! We're ending this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52731873826312192
    m_Localized: (Art by @Holidalo/Twitter)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52731967048912896
    m_Localized: Before you go, I'm incredibly grateful for people like you playing
      my game.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52731984061009920
    m_Localized: You are one of the few people that most likely managed to get this
      far to see this room.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52731988502777856
    m_Localized: This "two" year long journey has been very special to me, and I
      am happy to have been able to share it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52731992135045120
    m_Localized: From the bottom of my heart, thank you. I hope you've had your fun
      playing this stupid passion project of mine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52732008446693376
    m_Localized: And for those of you that can hear me. I can hear you, too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
